f performance is normal, use: `âœ… Good`\n- If CPA is high (e.g., > $65), use: `âš ï¸ High CPA`\n- If performance is clearly poor (e.g., very high CPA and low conversions), use: `ðŸš¨ Underperforming`\n\n**Key Recommendation Emoji and Bolding Rules:**\n- For recommendations about scaling up a successful campaign, use: `ðŸ† **Scale up**:`\n- For recommendations about optimizing a campaign to improve it, use: `âš ï¸ **Optimize**:`\n- For recommendations about reviewing a failing campaign, use: `ðŸš¨ **Review**:`\n\nHere is the JSON data for your analysis:\n{{ JSON.stringify($('Code1').item.json.allCampaigns) }}"
